%N A396313 Number of tilings of a 5 X n rectangle by unit squares and the Ferrers tile (3,3,2).
%C A396313 The Ferrers tile (3,3,2) has three columns of heights 3, 3, and 2.
%H A396313 Per Alexandersson and John Ahlberg, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.03473">Polynomials from tilings of rectangles</a>, arXiv:2605.03473 [math.CO], 2026.
